{"tid":1833274,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過一染三次頭髮","createTime":"2020-01-21T19:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T03:40:05.000Z","uid":27974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"984d0c278f51ce0a3b87f7f828b8690ee32be4dd","tid":1833274,"uid":27974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T19:44:49.000Z","msg":"睇唔順自己個布丁頭 今日去左salon染深啡色<br />\n<br />\n點知髮型師話要連續染兩次先染到<br />\n<br />\n好啦 染左3個幾鐘終於染完 點知又話染得唔平均要染多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最尾搞左5個鐘 染到黑色咁 依家頭皮有啲痕 頭髮又乾<br />\n<br />\n上網睇話唔可以連續染 又話會致癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人都試過連續染頭"},{"pid":"c4d4be2e16e2378fd098b9069d7f460ff4231dea","tid":1833274,"uid":30067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T19:47:30.000Z","msg":"頂盡兩次<br />\n條友好明顯做少左個步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0087b9b748050d525f9c8ba80e2221344a365a04","tid":1833274,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T20:12:17.000Z","msg":"好多時候失手都會咁樣 試過染紫色染左全日豆唔得 最後要第二日再去染 個頭就快爛"},{"pid":"cd3a56fbdfd5e21bfa6cea67cf6c3422bf3ee77f","tid":1833274,"uid":21137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T00:29:56.000Z","msg":"漂三次再染一次上色就試過，之後瘋狂做treatment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過幾個月去電，啲頭髮爛9哂"},{"pid":"00a22e45e216dd322403608685b86b4292f45d31","tid":1833274,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"我估佢揀隻藥水唔得所以上唔到色<br />\n你d頭髮頭皮已經好傷<br />\n快做多d保濕局油<br />\n停一排唔好染"}]}